<br />

<br />
I have never met or talked to Furor, I know zero about him and the only people I've talked to from FoH that I know of are, uh Ravvenn and only because she's a chanter.  I defend him in no way, I just felt like making a point thank you and have a nice day~</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Lelyia
